creator: rolleplayalt
descriptionHtml:
Quicksand Mods for Minecraft PE will add several new types of popular texture to the game. Also, the mod will add items with which you can get out of the new danger.
After installation, you will not notice how you step into a hole that can swallow you.
This addon has many more uses than it might seem at first glance. For example, you can surround your house with them. This will protect your building in the world of video games from unwanted guests and zombies. Do not forget to leave a path for yourself, otherwise you will find yourself in your own trap.
The app adds items to help itself and new texture packs.
Do not forget that you can play alone offline or use the multiplayer server and play online with other players.

Application features:
-continuous updates
- installation guide
-easy to download in one click
-suitable for girls
